Transport CAS Wavinya Ndeti has been drawn into a curious land battle in which the High Court declined to award the prime property along the Nairobi-Mombasa highway to any of the parties laying claim to it.
Tinek Limited and its director Abdinoor Shariff Ahmed have accused Ms Ndeti and a relative of hers identified as Peter Nzuki Ndeti of colluding with the National Land Commission (NLC) to fraudulently acquire the five acres in Athi River.



