After insisting that no hearing had been held, Ms Mbagaya called Ms Ndeti in the presence of Mr Ahmed. She told Mr Ahmed that he should discuss the case with Ms Ndeti. Mr Ahmed says in court papers that he was surprised to learn of a gazette notice quashing his title deed on November 9, 2018. He adds that even Mr Nzuki was unaware that there was a hearing or a decision made in the matter.



